* Iron Raptor roared as she got to her feet, nobot did that to her!!!
She snarled and spat, she was as raged as a bull seeing red! There was no 
way in the Inferno that this bot was going to get away with doing that to 
her and kicking her friend, none at all!
Iron Raptor came up behind Senesis and swing her sword at his side, she 
smiled as she felt the blade dig deeply! She twisted and shoved the blade 
deeper, now he would feel it!!*

" You should have made your move count, Predacon slag!!"

* She then reached behind her and pulled out a splatter gun, she pressed it 
to the back Sesesis's head with her free hand. Iron Raptor growled, this was 
for her friend! She pulled the trigger...*
